Ref:
When you pass the logical ID of this resource to the intrinsic Ref function, Ref returns the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the web ACL.

For more information about using the Ref function, see Ref.

GetAtt.Description: Indicates whether the logging configuration was created by AWS Firewall Manager, as  part of an AWS WAF policy configuration. If true, only Firewall Manager can modify or delete the configuration.
